\{A_k\}
\{B_k\}
\lim_{k \rightarrow \infty} A_k = A_{\infty}
\lim_{k \rightarrow \infty} B_k = B_{\infty}
A_k \cap B_k \neq \emptyset \; \forall k,
A_{\infty} \cap B_{\infty} \neq \emptyset
k\in\Bbb N
x_k\in A_k\cap B_k
\langle x_{n_k}:k\in\Bbb N\rangle
\langle x_n:n\in\Bbb N\rangle
a\in A_\infty
\langle x_{n_k}:k\in\Bbb N\rangle
b\in B_\infty
a=b\in A_\infty\cap B_\infty
